elements.name: Positive scenario for creating new patient

steps.name: User logged in, clicks register a patient button
User enters 'givenName', 'familyName' and clicks next button
User chooses his 'gender' and clicks next button
User enters his 'date','month','year' of birth and clicks next button
User enters his 'address' and clicks next button
User enters his 'phoneNumber' and clicks next button
User chooses his 'relationshipType', enter the 'name' and clicks next button
User validate his 'fullName','gender','birthday','address','phoneNumber','relationshipType' is displayed and clicks confirm button
User validate his 'fullName' and 'id' is displayed on his page
User clicks on home page and choose find patient record button
User enter his 'id' in search bar and validate his 'id' is unique
